sets.title: Powerhouse legs
sets.summary: Target your lower body for balance and powerhouse performance.
sets.subTitle: Centr Power in Gym: Advanced week 2

workouts.title: Workout
workouts.introText:
There's no skipping leg day! To truly make your legs a powerhouse you need to consistently work the same muscles.


Make your first stop the exercise tutorial to reset your form, then get thrusting.

groups.title: Warm-up
groups.summary: There are major muscle groups in your lower body, so get them primed to work.

groups.title: Round 1
groups.summary: This move engages your entire lower body and recruits your core for stabilization.

groups.title: Round 2
groups.summary: You'll need core control and balance to master these lunges.

groups.title: Round 3
groups.summary: Get those glutes and hamstrings firing.

groups.title: Round 4
groups.summary: Extensions will hit your quads for tough, muscular thighs.

groups.title: Round 5
groups.summary: Control the pace of lowering your calf to max the benefits.
